31:26.468 --> 31:29.595
The finest gladiators
in all of Capua.

31:29.763 --> 31:32.807
Hmm, a demonstration perhaps?

31:32.975 --> 31:34.809
Of course.

31:34.977 --> 31:37.144
Gannicus, step forward.

31:38.438 --> 31:40.982
Behold my finest champion.

31:41.149 --> 31:43.776
No man stands his equal.

31:43.944 --> 31:47.196
