who fought so bravely?

31:49.866 --> 31:51.742
What about the Gaul?

31:51.910 --> 31:54.161
Who would not marvel
at seeing such a creature

31:54.329 --> 31:56.247
locked in mortal embrace?

31:57.833 --> 32:00.668
Crixus? Apologies.

32:00.836 --> 32:03.004
The man does not yet bear
the mark of the brotherhood.

32:03.171 --> 32:04.463
Yet he is presented.

32:04.631 --> 32:07.341
I fear such a match
would be overly brief.

32:07.509 --> 32:09.260
